---
title: Sesame-Crumbed Pork & Veggie Fries with Sautéed Cabbage & Garlic Aioli
description: Schnitzel and chips is a classic, but this version’s had a makeover! Veggie fries are a twist on the typical, with carrot and parsnip bringing sweetness and colour. And let’s not forget the sautéed cabbage, cooked down with Asian flavours for a sweet and savoury finish. We think we’re on to a winner!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

